posting_body: ['entral Park Manor', '1510 Mainstreet, Hopkins, MN, 55305', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'CENTRAL PARK MANOR', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 660 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to Central Park Manor Apartments in Hopkins, Minnesota!', 'Central Park Manor offers one bedroom and two bedroom units in a 4 story building.', 'Enjoy our new fitness center, host a party in our party room, or visit with friends in our internet lounge.', 'Central Park Manor features underground parking and a great location nearby a local park with Tennis Courts, walking path and playground area.', 'Located in downtown Hopkins, just a short stroll to the performing arts center, movie theaters, restaurants, quaint coffee shops and shopping.', 'Call today to schedule your personal tour!', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'anzKfDZh93']
